pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">十二、经费：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">参赛各单位差旅费、住宿费自理。食宿由大会统一安排，大会指定住宿酒店如下，为便于竞赛组织，各参赛单位不得私自住宿其他酒店。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">酒店：四川中亚酒店</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>地址：成都市金牛区茶店子正街</span>132<span>号</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>价格：单</span>/<span>标间 &nbsp;</span><span>280</span><span>元</span><span>/</span><span>间（含早餐）</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">十三、未尽事宜另行通知。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;fon