#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">四、参赛单位：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>中国保龄球协会</span>A<span>级团体会员单位和经国家体育总局小球运动管理中心、中国保龄球协会批准的其他参赛单位。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">五、竞赛项目：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">团体：男子团体</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">男子：单人赛、双人赛、三人赛、五人队际贝克赛、全能、精英赛。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">六、参赛资格：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">参赛单位包括</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:69.75pt;color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:-42.75pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\">（一）&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">各省、自治区、直辖市、计划单列市、行业体协</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:27pt;color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">北方赛区包括：黑龙江省、吉林省、辽宁省、大连市、河北省、北京市、天津市、内蒙古自治区、山西省、山东省、河南省、安徽省、江苏省、新疆维吾尔自治区、青海省、甘肃省、宁夏回族自治区、陕西省、中央直属单位行业体育协会</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:69.75pt;color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:-42.75pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\">（二）&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">中国保龄球协会训练基地及青少年训练基地：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>北方赛区包括：中保协盐城训练基地、中保协沈阳青少年训练基地</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:69.75pt;color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:-42.75pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\">（三）&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">其它中国保龄球协会特批的参赛单位</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>北方赛区包括：承办单位等其它特批参赛单位</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">其中上述各省、自治区、直辖市参赛单位可派两支队伍参赛，其他参赛单位可派一支队伍参赛。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">参赛各单位运动员必须符合《中国保龄球协会会员管理规定》的要求，具备中国保龄球协会个人会员资格。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">七、竞赛办法：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（一）男子比赛：包括男子单人赛、双人赛、三人赛、五人队际贝克赛、全能、精英赛</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">1<span>、男子单项赛：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>1<span>）男子单人赛、双人赛、三人赛每人各打</span><span>6</span><span>局，分别以单人、双人、三人参赛选手</span><span>6</span><span>局得分之和，按得分高低排列名次。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>2<span>）男子三人赛分为两节进行，比赛分别用两种油型两天完成。两节比赛之间两组选手不可换人，但可以调换投球顺序。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>3<span>）男子五人队际赛分为预赛和决赛，均采用贝克式打法，预赛进行两节（每节</span><span>9</span><span>局）共</span><span>18</span><span>局比赛，两节比赛分别用两种油型两天完成。五人赛每一节各队均派出五名选手参赛，一名选手轮空，两节比赛之间可以换人及调换投球顺序。预赛按</span><span>18</span><span>局总分高低排列名次，取前四名进入决赛，决赛采用交叉淘汰赛方式进行，半决赛采用一局一胜制，冠亚军决赛采用三局两胜制。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>4<span>）贝克式打法指本队参赛成员按照每人一格的投球顺序完成一局比赛，比赛期间不允许更换投球顺序。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:23.25pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">2<span>、男子全能成绩：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:23.25pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>各参赛选手单人、双人、三人赛共</span>18<span>局比赛合计分计算全能分数，按得分高低排列全能名次。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">3<span>、同分裁决：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>1<span>）男子单人赛、双人赛、三人赛及全能积分相同需要区分名次时，采用突然死亡法，即双方或多方按照投球顺序进行</span><span>1</span><span>次投球，投出全中的获得比赛胜利，同为全中或者同为不全中则按照投球顺序继续投球，直至分出胜负。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>2<span>）男子五人队际赛预赛、决赛需要区分名次或胜负时，采用点球决胜方式如下：按照投球顺序轮流进行</span><span>1</span><span>轮投球，即五人赛每队投五球。</span><span>1</span><span>轮投球结束后按全中数量区分胜负，全中数量相同则按照投球顺序两队各投一球，击出全中的队伍获胜，如均击出全中或均未击出全中，则继续进行投球直至决出胜负。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:23.25pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">4<span>、男子精英赛：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:23.25pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>1<span>）获得个人全能</span><span>18</span><span>局总分前</span><span>8</span><span>名选手参加精英赛（每队最多进入</span><span>2</span><span>人）。进入精英赛的运动员，于精英赛比赛的前一天到竞赛部确认是否参加精英赛比赛。凡未确认者其名次位置由相邻名次依次递补，最终确认</span><span>8</span><span>名运动员参加精英赛比赛。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>（</span>2<span>）</span><span>8</span><span>名运动员按照全能成绩排名进行交叉对抗赛，即第一名对抗第八名，第二名对抗第七名，以此类推。比赛采用</span><span>3</span><span>局</span><span>2</span><span>胜决胜负，胜者晋级。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>3<span>）晋级的</span><span>4</span><span>名运动员按照全能成绩排名进行交叉对抗，胜者进入决赛，负者并列第三名，比赛采用</span><span>3</span><span>局两</span><span>2</span><span>制。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>4<span>）进入决赛的</span><span>2</span><span>名运动员采用</span><span>3</span><span>局</span><span>2</span><span>胜制决出最终的冠亚军。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>5<span>）精英赛每轮比赛均由全能排名靠前的选手选择首局比赛油型及投球顺序，随后的比赛依次交替。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>6<span>）如在一局比赛中出现同分，采用“突然死亡法”，双方在同一条球道上各投一球，先投出全中者获胜，如同时未投出或投出全中，继续投球直至决出胜负。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>（四）男子团体总分计算办法：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:23.25pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>男子团体成绩：男子报名须报满</span>6<span>人。男子团体成绩由下述</span><span>2</span><span>项成绩之和构成（全部为同分裁决之前，也就是说可能产生并列名次），按由高至低排列名次。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:23.25pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>1<span>）最好的</span><span>5</span><span>名选手的全能成绩</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:23.25pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（</span>2<span>）五人队际赛预赛成绩</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:23.25pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">如出现成绩相同需要区分名次，按各类别单项获得金牌数区分，如所获金牌数相同，则按照所获得银牌数区分，以此类推。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>（五）最高局分出现同分时，以最早出现的最高局分为准。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">八、规则、裁判员及仲裁：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>比赛采用</span>2017<span>年中国保龄球协会审定的</span><span>World Bowling</span><span>竞赛规则。由三人组成技术委员会主持比赛，由三人组成仲裁委员会依据</span><span>World Bowling</span><span>相关规定执行仲裁职责。裁判及仲裁人选另行通知。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">球检：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"><span>所有参赛者必须参加球检，以确保其比赛用球符合</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">World Bowling</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"><span>竞赛规则关于保龄球的数量、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">球的表面，球的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"><span>重量及其他方面的有关规定</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">比赛赛区内严禁吸烟。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">九、录取名次及奖励：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（一）男子单人赛、双人赛、三人赛、队际赛各奖励前六名，精英赛奖励前八名。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（二）设男子最高局分奖。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（三）设</span>\"<span>体育道德风尚奖</span><span>\"</span><span>（办法另定）。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（四）男子团体冠军奖杯一座，男子团体总分前六名将获得参加全国男子保龄球锦标赛总决赛的资格。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">十、注册、报名、报到及相关处罚：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（一）注册：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">1<span>、注册周期：全国保龄球锦标赛将采用比赛年度注册制度，注册日自本年度首个比赛报名日起至次年度首个比赛报名日止。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">2<span>、参赛单位参赛运动员必须报满男子</span><span>6</span><span>人，全部比赛每个参赛单位（包括允许报两支队伍的参赛单位）仅允许注册２名外籍运动员（非本省（市）参赛运动员），外籍运动员必须签订代表关系协议并由参赛单位至中保协备案，非省、自治区、直辖市参赛队伍按其训练基地、行业体协、公司注册所在地等确定其参赛单位地域归属，计划单列市、训练基地等市级参赛单位外籍运动员指非本所在省运动员。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">3<span>、运动员通过本人身份证或居住证明确定是否属于外籍运动员，各参赛队提交报名表时必须填写参赛人员身份证号码或提交有效居住证明（长期居住于本地区运动员）。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">4<span>、全部比赛实行唯一注册制度，即一名运动员仅能选择一个参赛单位的一支参赛队伍进行注册。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">5<span>、男子比赛中，每支参赛队伍须至少包括一名</span><span>25</span><span>周岁以下选手（</span><span>1992</span><span>年</span><span>1</span><span>月</span><span>1</span><span>日以后出生）</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">6<span>、获得男子总决赛资格的参赛队伍在总决赛前最多可更换２名未注册过的运动员，但仍须符合上述全部注册报名要求。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">7<span>、中国保龄球协会将就上述注册报名要求进行严格核查，运动员报到时一并审查身份证原件及代表资格，如出现弄虚作假等行为，将予以取消其参赛资格并保留进一步追加处罚的权力。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（二）报名：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">本次全国保龄球锦标赛报名规定如下：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">1<span>、各参赛单位可报领队</span><span>2</span><span>名（其中当地体育局或保协官员至少</span><span>1</span><span>名），教练员</span><span>2</span><span>名，男队必须报满</span><span>6</span><span>人。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">2<span>、请各参赛单位按竞赛规程要求，填写其后所附预报名表，并加盖所属体育局或协会公章，于</span><span>5</span><span>月</span><span>15</span><span>日前扫描并发送至指定报名邮箱（联系人：王佳鑫</span><span>010-87182483</span><span>，王姝</span><span>13842879621</span><span>，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"><span>邮箱</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">yayunbaoling@163.com</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"><span>），邮件名命名为</span>“201</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">7<span>年全国男子锦标赛北方赛区</span><span>***</span><span>队预报名表”。经审核无误后，参赛单位须于</span><span>5</span><span>月</span><span>31</span><span>日前将最终报名表命名为</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\">“201</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">7<span>年全国男子锦标赛北方赛区</span><span>***</span><span>队最终报名表”扫描并发送至上述邮箱，逾期报名无效。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（三）报到：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>各参赛单位男子于</span>2017<span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月</span><span>15</span><span>日到赛区报到，</span><span>16</span><span>日球检、练习、召开领队技术会议，</span><span>6</span><span>月</span><span>17</span><span>日至</span><span>6</span><span>月</span><span>21</span><span>日比赛，</span><span>6</span><span>月</span><span>22</span><span>日离会</span><span>。报到地点：长春欧亚保龄球馆，地址：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>长春市开运街</span>5178号欧亚卖场四层，联系人：王姝13842879621。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">如有提前报到者，必须征得承办单位同意，所需经费自理。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>（四）处罚：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">自报名受理之日起，凡无故中途退出比赛的单位和个人，均停赛一年。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">十一、服装和器材：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（一）比赛时各队应按照</span>World Bowling<span>规定，统一队服。在比赛服装上可以出现：</span><span>1.&nbsp;</span><span>运动员姓名；</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">2.&nbsp;<span>省市地区名称；</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">3.&nbsp;<span>运动员所代表的省市地区协会的标志；</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.&nbsp;<span>呈现在服装上的广告，大小不得超过运动员服装背后字体大小的一半，且内容必须遵守国家有关法律和规定。为协调各方面利益，本次比赛规定各参赛队以及大会主赞助商的服装广告均不得具有唯一性。各参赛队服装广告队名前如冠企业名称，总字数应不超过</span><span>8</span><span>个字。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（二）自带符合竞赛规则的保龄球和鞋。比赛用球通过球检，方可使用。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（三）下油标准：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">2017<span>年全国保龄球锦标赛比赛油型与</span><span>2016</span><span>年全国保龄球锦标赛比赛油型相同。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（四）保龄球瓶重量符合</span>World Bowling<span>规则规定。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">十二、经费：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&