FF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>价格：</span>279<span>元</span><span>/</span><span>天</span><span>.</span><span>间（含双早）</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">十三、未尽事宜另行通知。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:18pt;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">十四、本规程解释权属国家体育总局小球运动管理中心、中国保龄球协会。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>','2','','','1498877574','1501469557','0','','2','0','1501257600','1501516799','吉林','长春市','宽城区','蜀蓉路116号（距球馆步行15分钟）','uploads/ico/14988775439032.jpg','a:1:{i:0;s:1:\"3\";}','a:2:{s:5:\"file2\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"成绩单\";s:3:\"src\";s:0:\"\";}}s:5:\"file1\";s:69:\"uploads/2017/07/59570edda0e39.jpeg|uploads/2017/07/59570ee153bd8.jpeg\";}','')
